@TOC "rexx.guide/Built-In FUNCTION LIBRARY INDEX"
@{b}FIND()@{ub}

Usage:@{b}FIND(string,pattern)@{ub}

Finds the pattern in string and returns the word position of the first
match, or 0 if there is no match.

   Examples:
   @{fg shine}
         SAY FIND('Tied to Godot?','dot')  ->  0
         SAY FIND('Tied to Godot?','to')   ->  2
   @{fg text}
@ENDNODE
